{"tid":2237153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全民感謝日　千五黃店自救","createTime":"2020-10-10T04:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T04:45:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8913172bf942eff498a136a621611008547899","tid":2237153,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/FE54MHBRCRB7JIDT2FTFTPOGHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FFE54MHBRCRB7JIDT2FTFTPOGHE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4b156a99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FFE54MHBRCRB7JIDT2FTFTPOGHE%2F&h=71557f2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/FE54MHBRCRB7JIDT2FTFTPOGHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全民感謝日 千五黃店自救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Kx_RScsZPAEvaoIBzRQJ65zjCF4=/4924x3282/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H2AR3QTCRNCBBD4YG6QQXJOGMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKx_RScsZPAEvaoIBzRQJ65zjCF4%3D%2F4924x3282%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH2AR3QTCRNCBBD4YG6QQXJOGMQ.jpg&h=943b7421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■食肆桔梗有全民感謝日，負責人寄語港人不要「鬥黃」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃色經濟圈建立至今，在政權打壓與武漢肺炎夾擊下頻頻告急。黃店決定自救，今明兩天辦「10.10全民感謝日」，冀民間自救力撐黃店，同時喚醒港人毋忘初心，繼續以消費選擇未來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HimlV-rq_BZwjqzJpV4cjCb5ZIQ=/899x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LSIMHXIDSBBYNJMIYF3F7PFUCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHimlV-rq_BZwjqzJpV4cjCb5ZIQ%3D%2F899x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLSIMHXIDSBBYNJMIYF3F7PFUCY.jpg&h=f907adab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團隊促港人毋忘初衷<br />\n<br />\n參與全民感謝日的黃店在昨突破1,500間。籌備團隊在社交平台指，近月有店舖反映堅持光顧黃店人數減少，早前甚至有知名連鎖冰室結業，反映黃色經濟圈處於危急存亡之秋，希望透過活動喚醒港人支持黃店初衷。<br />\n<br />\n活動亦有網店參與，香城雜貨是其中一員。。。。。。。。。。，寄語港人「堅持先有希望」。<br />\n<br />\n食肆桔梗負責人Ivan亦聞有黃店結業，同時留意到藍店食肆重現人龍。他希望港人不要「鬥黃」，明白有人或對部份黃店處事手法有意見，但應先「槍頭一致向外」。他對黃色經濟圈仍感樂觀，相信港人仍會支持黃店。活動內容及店舖名單可參閱「10.10全民感謝日」facebook專頁。"}]}